  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This initiative supports the Disaster Risk Reduction and Resilience Building Program in rural and urban sectors of India to respond to climate change. This will focus on disaster risk reduction in urban slums with a particular focus on vulnerable communities. Support will also be provided to foster national level work that facilitates local humanitarian leaders, particularly women and girls. This initiative also entails state and national advocacy on disaster risk reduction and inter-agency coordination.</narrative>
